name: Nssktkslis
content:
Doctor Nssktkslis was a cybernetic specialist who operated out of the Mos Entha medical center.
Nssktkslis was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. In the game, all three cybernetic specialists were erroneously identified as Aboo Aramflahad. However, the Friday Feature titled Review of Cybernetics identified the Nssktkslis as the Trandoshan working in Mos Entha, and the other two as Aboo Aramflahad and Mindt F'abul.
